column8: This charming  room is spacious and flooded with natural light! You have your own private bathroom (with bathtub) and the toilet is separate. A nice double bed with a view over the meadow. There is a (2p) sofa bed, should that be necessary for additional guests. You'll also find a fridge, TV, Nespresso coffee machine, kettle, and...an egg cooker. Egg of the land!accommodation has a stylish decor.

column7: Flat with garden in Oud West, Amsterdam
column8:
The flat:
60m2 space that includes one double bedroom with a double bed, single bedroom, kitchen, bathroom with bath/shower, bright open space living/dining area and private garden (approx 35m2)!

The area:
Situated in the Kinkerbuurt in Oud West. You are on the doorstep of de Hallen, a plethora of cafes & restaurants and a local market (Ten Kate Markt).

Getting about:
Well connected with trams 3, 7, 13, 17 & 19 all within 2 minutes walk or nice stroll to the centre.

column8: Nice, spacious and light apartment in the vibrant area of 'de Baarsjes'. Close to public transport 10 minutes to the very center of Amsterdam.

column7: Great modern apartment near Amsterdam center.
column8:
Lovely apartment at a great location. Itâ€™s situated between the city center (10 min walk) and Artis Zoo (10 min walk). Within 5 minutes you can visit the Oosterpark.

The apartment is a two level maisonnette on the 3rd floor of the building (no elevator).

There is a kingsize bed and the possibility to add another one or two person bed. Also suitable for families with babies as all facilities are available.

Easy access by public transportation as the metro/tram station are near.

column8:
Lovely holiday house in the picturesque and quiet district of Kadoelen, max. 10 minutes by bike from NDSM Pont or Buiksloterweg.

The sunny villa is located on the water and with the kayak or sup you can sail a bit towards the nature park 't Twiske.

The relaxed sun beds and luxury gas BBQ at the jetty ensure the optimal summer atmosphere.

The spacious living room with adjoining kitchen is equipped with all the comforts (oven, microwave and dishwasher). You can also relax in the conservatory.
